## 6. Audit Rights

The Licensor reserves the right to:

* Request reasonable documentation to verify compliance with revenue thresholds and usage terms.
* Conduct audits with reasonable notice.

Failure to comply with audit requests constitutes a breach of this license.

If an audit reveals an underpayment of more than 5% for any audited period, the User must promptly pay the underpaid amount, accrued interest, and reasonable audit costs.

